PlayerData Class
DataStore.Structure("Players", player.SteamID: playerData)

playerData = {'name': self.playerName,
                            'tribe': self.playerTribe,
                            'online': self.playerOnlineStatus,
                            'tribeRank': self.playerTribeRank,
                            'pendingInvites' : 'No pending invites'
                           }

TribeData Class
DataStore.Structure("Tribes", tribeName, tribeData)

tribeData = {'creatorID': '',
            'tribeMembers': [],
            'tribeFriends': [],
            'tribeEnemies' : [],
            'tribeRaidable': bool
        }


Glavna klasa bi trebala imati instancu svih playera i tribeova:
players = PlayerData.Keys('Players')
tribes = TribeData.Keys('Tribes')

U tom sluèaju bi modifikacije po DataStore vrijednostima mogao vršiti preko tih instanci, umjesto da ih inicijaliziram prilikom svake potrebe za promjenama